at can be produced from these elements is almost infinite! Originality and strategy that confuse and confound your opponent are the keys to victory. Your custom Shots can be shared worldwide through the Steam Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/ad5fd7e493c2c38b4ab13859b2b8f862.webp?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/3c52eddde719a64a929fdc2e48cc3f5c.avif?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br>In single-player \"Quest Mode\", you will participate in the League of Crafters as a novice wizard. Aim to dominate at the yearly tournament that determines the best of all the Magic Knights. You can acquire new Shots as you battle your way through the Quest Mode, then use these Shots as they are, or as a template for further custom development.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/6122efc08304fc9c7604795d5fc138de.webp?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/557d6c05a61a6bdb950364822a32d7cc.avif?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=172 /></span><br>The battle mode supports local / online multiplayer. You can play casually with friends or compete with players around the world through random matching.",
